## Selection Criteria

Each segment should satisfy multiple of the following conditions:
- Contains a clear, counter-intuitive, or thought-provoking point
- Supported by concrete examples, data, or stories
- Can be explained clearly within 15-60 seconds
- Works well as a short video opening (strong hook)
- Has quote potential (can be quoted on its own)

